reviewText: These movies were made in the early 60s with two of great rock singers; Enrique Guzman, and Cesar Costa. If you enjoy music of that era you will enjoy these two movies. Note there are no English subtitles, only Spanish spoken, Mexican video production.
There is a mistake on Amazon information regarding code region 14 for the DVD, there is no such thing, please check the back of the case, and you will see region 1, and region 4 separately printed.
